nikto as a web server scanner - open source replacement for netsparker, acunetix, et.al.
You might be better off using Burp (free version) and seeing what you get.
This is the equivalent of using a sword to fight a fly.
https://cirt.net/Nikto2

mkdir /usr/share/nikto
cd /usr/share/nikto
wget https://github.com/sullo/nikto/archive/master.zip
tar -xvzf master.zip
nikto -C all -h http://IPAddress
